This paper discusses the use of patent maps and interactive overlay techniques to analyze innovation dynamics, which involves data analysis and visualization. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Digital Libraries (cs.DL), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Social and Information Networks (cs.SI), Cybernetics (cs.CY), and Sound (cs.SD).
